# /models — Database schema definitions & ORM model classes
# Defines the shape of each PostgreSQL table using Sequelize / Prisma / Knex.
# Examples:
#   User.js            → id, name, email, passwordHash, role, createdAt
#   Emission.js        → id, userId, category, value, unit, date, source
#   Report.js          → id, userId, title, dateRange, generatedAt, fileUrl
#   Category.js        → id, name, emissionFactor, unit (transport, energy, etc.)
#   index.js           → Model associations & relationship definitions
